messages.message: Does anyone know how to fix this?

Update:
```pre-commit uninstall && pip install pre-commit --upgrade && pre-commit install  ```
this fixed it, so I think the pre-commit in the base crafting image is out-of-date.

I spoke too soon :laugh-cry:
